Enum CommandWord

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Enum<CommandWord>
      CommandWord
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<CommandWord>
public enum CommandWord
extends Enum<CommandWord>
implements Serializable

Representations for all the valid command words in the Cinema Booking System along with their number of parameters. Each command word is associated with a string in a particular language and the minimum number of parameters needed for that command.

Version:
01.11.10
Author:
Fariha Nazmul
